data.description: Do you like a subdivision but want some acreage & peace? North Ridge is perfect for you. This 4 bed, 3 bath home has space & seclusion. The home is located on a cul-de-sac with 4.06 acres, & a massive 40x80 shop. The 2-car garage also boasts a bonus room above it. As you enter the front door you are greeted with a dining room & tiered ceiling. A brief distance is the living room with fireplace & kitchen area. Upstairs there are 2 bedrooms & 2 baths. The downstairs has 2 separate stair access points, from east & west end. Downstairs there is an additional bed & bathroom with a hobby room, safe room & multiple bonus rooms for your heart's desire.
